citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:45 to 3:10
pm on 27-Nov-17.
Inspectors arrived at 1:45 pm to a locked gate. Inspector honked horn and called both listed numbers leaving
message. Inspectors waited to 3:10 pm.
Additional Inspectors
Vernon Kathryn, Animal Care Inspector
